ns from the CMB and\nthe dust disk, respectively, by electrons in both the blazar core and sub-kpc\njet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Oct 2021 18:59:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Oct 2021 15:00:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-13"}
